    {
      "text": "A helicopter flying simulation for the DS, with seventeen different missions to fly and shoot a helicopter through.\n\nFly heavily armed helicopter gunships through more than 10 fast-paced action-packed missions in Blades of Thunder 2. Fight a multiplayer Free-For-All dogfight with up to six players over wireless LAN. Plot your attack via touch screen during pre-mission planning stages, where you can reinforce posts, purchase intelligence, armor, and engine upgrades.",
